cs.NI, cs.MA, cs.IT, cs.CR, cs.DC 

This paper discusses the use of mobile entities to carry data and create a communication channel, which is a topic related to network infrastructure (cs.NI) and mobile computing (cs.MA). The paper also discusses the use of this communication channel to overcome limitations of conventional data networks, which is related to information theory (cs.IT) and cryptography (cs.CR). Finally, the paper discusses the deployment of ad hoc networks in challenging environments, which is related to distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC).
